WEBVTT

00:00:11.991 --> 00:00:13.034
You must be cold.

00:00:56.244 --> 00:01:00.832
Ms. Seo Mi-rae, your one-month free trial
of Boyfriend on Demand has ended.

00:01:01.583 --> 00:01:02.542
No.

00:01:03.334 --> 00:01:04.586
No!

00:01:06.546 --> 00:01:07.839
Don't go.

00:01:08.339 --> 00:01:09.674
No. You can't!

00:01:12.343 --> 00:01:13.678
Eun-ho…

00:01:14.345 --> 00:01:16.431
Don't let it end like this!

00:01:16.514 --> 00:01:17.932
No!

00:01:18.016 --> 00:01:19.517
SERVICE PERIOD EXPIRED

00:01:20.727 --> 00:01:21.936
Eun-ho!

00:01:26.941 --> 00:01:28.234
TRIAL ENDED

00:01:37.994 --> 00:01:39.120
Eun-ho…

00:01:42.957 --> 00:01:44.626
Evil bastards.

00:01:50.548 --> 00:01:56.054
Ms. Seo Mi-rae, please give a star rating
for your second date, Seo Eun-ho.

00:01:59.933 --> 00:02:03.937
HOW WAS YOUR DATE WITH SEO EUN-HO
IN &lt;SPRING, AND YOU&gt;?

00:02:04.020 --> 00:02:05.647
THANK YOU FOR PARTICIPATING

00:02:10.944 --> 00:02:11.861
No!

00:02:11.945 --> 00:02:13.529
EPISODE 4
NO RISK, HIGH RETURN

00:02:14.030 --> 00:02:15.740
ONE MONTH LATER

00:02:16.532 --> 00:02:20.954
The short-lived dream came to an end,
and I returned to my life.

00:02:21.829 --> 00:02:24.832
Awesome. TMTK and PlanC
are crushing it right now.

00:02:25.416 --> 00:02:29.921
Just as Yun Song said, her readers indeed
loved to hate-read out of habit,

00:02:30.004 --> 00:02:32.799
and The Man to Know did not fall easily.

00:02:33.341 --> 00:02:35.343
A long-running webtoon like TMTK is…

00:02:35.426 --> 00:02:38.304
But, of course,
I must never let my guard down.

00:02:38.388 --> 00:02:41.557
The next agenda is… Yes, the contest.

00:02:41.641 --> 00:02:43.268
It's that season again.

00:02:43.351 --> 00:02:46.562
This time, I didn't assign the genres
based on teams.

00:02:46.646 --> 00:02:49.065
I've personally allocated each of you.

00:02:49.691 --> 00:02:53.861
So, first up, fantasy.

00:02:54.445 --> 00:02:56.864
Choi Dong-min. Kim Seon-jeong.
You two are on it.

00:02:57.490 --> 00:02:58.324
-Okay.
-Okay.

00:02:58.408 --> 00:03:00.451
As for romantasy,

00:03:01.369 --> 00:03:03.621
Seo Mi-rae and

00:03:04.539 --> 00:03:06.416
Park Kyeong-nam. Congrats.

00:03:08.042 --> 00:03:10.628
Next, we have action.

00:03:12.338 --> 00:03:13.798
I let my guard down.

00:03:16.009 --> 00:03:17.719
Why was it you and not me?

00:03:17.802 --> 00:03:20.388
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

00:03:21.097 --> 00:03:22.598
I don't know either.

00:03:22.682 --> 00:03:24.017
Does he hate you or something?

00:03:24.600 --> 00:03:26.936
He's put you with Yun Song
and the nastiest genre.

00:03:27.020 --> 00:03:29.439
I'm asking why I wasn't picked.

00:03:29.522 --> 00:03:31.232
It's the most important genre.

00:03:31.316 --> 00:03:34.694
He handed it to those in charge of
the hottest webtoons right now.

00:03:34.777 --> 00:03:35.695
It's only natural.

00:03:35.778 --> 00:03:37.447
Just have some of this.

00:03:38.197 --> 00:03:40.950
Good on you for snagging us seats
far from the director.

00:03:41.034 --> 00:03:43.244
I had to camp out to get this table.

00:03:44.996 --> 00:03:45.913
Here.

00:03:46.914 --> 00:03:49.083
Hey, why have you been so down lately?

00:03:50.001 --> 00:03:50.835
Me?

00:03:52.378 --> 00:03:53.963
-Have I?
-Yeah.

00:03:54.464 --> 00:03:55.965
I noticed that too.

00:03:56.049 --> 00:03:58.551
Even at lunchtime, you seemed kind of

00:03:58.634 --> 00:04:00.303
wistful, I guess?

00:04:01.429 --> 00:04:05.058
Maybe she's just lonely.
It's almost the end of the year.

00:04:05.558 --> 00:04:06.642
Already?

00:04:07.310 --> 00:04:11.147
I've got a friend who's totally awesome.
Want me to set you up?

00:04:11.856 --> 00:04:14.984
If you start meeting up now,
you'll be dating by Christmas for sure.

00:04:15.068 --> 00:04:16.611
Yeah, set her up.

00:04:17.195 --> 00:04:18.946
-A blind date?
-He's younger than you.

00:04:19.030 --> 00:04:20.198
I have a picture of him.

00:04:21.616 --> 00:04:22.784
I'm good.

00:04:22.867 --> 00:04:25.536
Why not? You should accept these things
when you can.

00:04:25.620 --> 00:04:27.413
Well, I think I'm good.

00:04:27.497 --> 00:04:29.207
-Here it is!
-Let me see.

00:04:30.333 --> 00:04:32.251
Isn't he a catch?

00:04:32.335 --> 00:04:35.797
-Hey, he's so fine!
-Right?

00:04:35.880 --> 00:04:36.714
But

00:04:37.632 --> 00:04:39.467
you're already seeing someone.

00:04:40.718 --> 00:04:41.761
Who is?

00:04:43.471 --> 00:04:44.389
Ms. Seo.

00:04:45.223 --> 00:04:46.265
-Huh?
-What?

00:04:47.308 --> 00:04:49.185
-Nah!
-Nah!

00:04:50.186 --> 00:04:52.522
Wait, what are you talking about?

00:04:52.605 --> 00:04:57.235
You told me you had a date last time,
so I thought you had a boyfriend.

00:04:59.153 --> 00:05:03.157
Please, that was ages ago.
It was just a date, nothing serious.

00:05:04.659 --> 00:05:08.079
I mean, I got introduced to a guy
a while back.

00:05:08.162 --> 00:05:09.497
It was really brief.

00:05:10.164 --> 00:05:13.000
I see. I must have misunderstood.

00:05:14.001 --> 00:05:15.586
Ms. Seo, you wound me.

00:05:15.670 --> 00:05:17.088
-Huh?
-Me too.

00:05:17.171 --> 00:05:20.591
I knew you had clear boundaries,
but this one quite stings.

00:05:21.342 --> 00:05:25.138
No, I never mentioned it
because it really was nothing.

00:05:25.221 --> 00:05:28.141
She doesn't have to tell us
every little detail about her dates.

00:05:28.224 --> 00:05:29.308
Still…

00:05:30.476 --> 00:05:33.980
Anyway, does that mean
you're not seeing anyone right now?

00:05:34.480 --> 00:05:35.314
I'm not.

00:05:35.398 --> 00:05:37.275
How about that blind date? Go, go?

00:05:37.358 --> 00:05:38.776
-Go, go.
-Go, go.

00:05:42.071 --> 00:05:42.989
No, I'm good.

00:05:43.072 --> 00:05:44.407
That's it. Don't set her up.

00:05:44.490 --> 00:05:47.285
I get it.
She might not be into younger guys.

00:05:48.286 --> 00:05:50.329
Younger guys are my thing, you know.

00:05:50.830 --> 00:05:52.081
Would you like to take it?

00:05:53.124 --> 00:05:56.210
Well, you can show me that picture again.

00:05:56.294 --> 00:05:57.170
Sure.

00:05:58.421 --> 00:05:59.589
Where does he live?

00:05:59.672 --> 00:06:00.756
He lives in Seoul.

00:06:00.840 --> 00:06:02.675
I knew it. I live in Seoul too.

00:06:02.758 --> 00:06:04.135
-Isn't it great?
-It is.

00:06:04.218 --> 00:06:06.929
I've always preferred Seoul guys.
They live nearby and all.

00:06:07.805 --> 00:06:09.557
Why, that little…

00:06:12.602 --> 00:06:14.270
Man, aren't you cold?

00:06:14.353 --> 00:06:15.771
Hey, let's go!

00:06:15.855 --> 00:06:18.107
Thank you for the meal!

00:06:18.191 --> 00:06:19.442
See you all tomorrow!

00:06:21.277 --> 00:06:22.195
I've got to run.

00:06:22.278 --> 00:06:24.238
Hey, I'm buying. How about round two?

00:06:24.322 --> 00:06:25.531
-Round two, it is.
-Where…

00:06:25.615 --> 00:06:27.116
-Where are you going?
-Good night.

00:06:27.200 --> 00:06:28.034
Guys?

00:06:28.117 --> 00:06:29.869
-I'll be going, then.
-All right.

00:06:29.952 --> 00:06:31.204
Have a good night!

00:06:36.501 --> 00:06:37.835
-Where are you headed?
-What?

00:06:38.336 --> 00:06:40.254
Oh, I'm struggling to get a cab.

00:06:40.755 --> 00:06:43.257
Same. I'm sure we'll catch one on the way.

00:06:45.676 --> 00:06:46.511
Did

00:06:47.261 --> 00:06:49.597
what I said earlier bother you?

00:06:50.556 --> 00:06:51.682
Sorry?

00:06:51.766 --> 00:06:55.603
You know, how I brought up
your private life in front of everyone.

00:06:57.772 --> 00:06:59.774
It's fine. It was just a misunderstanding.

00:07:00.608 --> 00:07:03.110
Sorry about that.
I'm a bit slow on the uptake.

00:07:03.194 --> 00:07:04.946
You just realized that?

00:07:06.113 --> 00:07:07.281
I see.

00:07:10.326 --> 00:07:12.828
I look forward to
judging the submissions with you.

00:07:13.454 --> 00:07:15.873
Did you know we would be teamed up?

00:07:15.957 --> 00:07:16.958
No, I didn't.

00:07:18.876 --> 00:07:22.547
If you want to change partners,
we can talk to the director together.

00:07:23.297 --> 00:07:25.299
-You hate it that much?
-Huh?

00:07:25.383 --> 00:07:26.801
Having to judge with me.

00:07:29.095 --> 00:07:30.596
No, it's not like that.

00:07:31.180 --> 00:07:33.683
Then… let's do it together.

00:07:37.979 --> 00:07:39.438
I see taxis.

00:07:43.234 --> 00:07:45.027
Take the first one.

00:07:46.737 --> 00:07:47.863
Are you sure?

00:07:48.823 --> 00:07:49.657
What do you mean?

00:07:51.826 --> 00:07:52.660
Go ahead.

00:07:54.078 --> 00:07:56.247
Okay, then. Have a nice weekend.

00:07:56.330 --> 00:07:58.082
Right. You too.

00:07:58.165 --> 00:07:59.375
Cold!

00:08:03.713 --> 00:08:05.089
Hi. Yongsan, please.

00:08:05.590 --> 00:08:06.674
I don't go there.

00:08:07.174 --> 00:08:08.175
What?

00:08:08.259 --> 00:08:11.178
This is an Incheon taxi.
You should've looked before getting in.

00:08:12.972 --> 00:08:14.181
Sorry.

00:08:18.185 --> 00:08:19.562
INCHEON

00:08:21.063 --> 00:08:22.982
Are you kidding me?

00:08:23.649 --> 00:08:24.900
You could've told me!

00:08:40.082 --> 00:08:43.377
"I look forward to working with you"?
Could've fooled me.

00:08:51.552 --> 00:08:53.804
1: THE MAN TO KNOW
2: PlanC

00:08:53.888 --> 00:08:55.890
Always on our tail.
It's making me nervous.

00:08:58.726 --> 00:09:00.686
Here to cleanse my eyes
of the rotten TMTK.

00:09:00.770 --> 00:09:02.438
TMTK beat this? The system's rigged.

00:09:02.521 --> 00:09:04.690
Hwany is a god. PlanC is god-tier!

00:09:04.774 --> 00:09:06.609
JI-YEON

00:09:07.109 --> 00:09:09.362
Hey. What's up? It's late.

00:09:09.445 --> 00:09:11.947
Why haven't you been replying
in the group chat?

00:09:13.157 --> 00:09:14.617
I must've missed it. What is it?

00:09:14.700 --> 00:09:16.535
-You know it's tomorrow, right?
-Huh?

00:09:17.286 --> 00:09:19.121
An Da-yeong's housewarming party.

00:09:21.916 --> 00:09:23.042
Right.

00:09:23.542 --> 00:09:25.086
I knew this would happen.

00:09:25.169 --> 00:09:26.337
Don't forget.

00:09:28.464 --> 00:09:29.507
See you tomorrow.

00:09:34.679 --> 00:09:36.180
What should I buy?

00:09:40.226 --> 00:09:41.519
-Over there.
-Look at this.

00:09:41.602 --> 00:09:43.437
Oh my God!

00:09:44.438 --> 00:09:46.148
-Enjoy your time.
-Thank you.

00:09:46.232 --> 00:09:47.650
-Thank you.
-Excuse me.

00:09:47.733 --> 00:09:49.360
Is an idol coming here?

00:09:49.860 --> 00:09:53.239
No, this is the line
for the Boyfriend on Demand pop-up store.

00:09:54.699 --> 00:09:56.534
BOYFRIEND ON DEMAND
ENTRY NUMBER 454

00:10:01.747 --> 00:10:03.499
Right this way!

00:10:08.587 --> 00:10:11.048
-Let me show you.
-Would you like to try it on?

00:10:20.015 --> 00:10:21.225
Ms. Seo?

00:10:22.643 --> 00:10:23.894
-Hello.
-Hi there.

00:10:24.478 --> 00:10:25.730
How nice of you to come.

00:10:25.813 --> 00:10:27.898
I could have reserved you a spot.

00:10:27.982 --> 00:10:30.693
No, I just happened to be passing by.

00:10:30.776 --> 00:10:31.610
Is that so?

00:10:32.236 --> 00:10:35.614
Yes. This is quite a turnout.

00:10:35.698 --> 00:10:37.158
Yes. Isn't it amazing?

00:10:37.950 --> 00:10:41.370
We should have the highest sales
of any pop-up here this year.

00:10:43.164 --> 00:10:44.623
Congratulations, Mr. Min.

00:10:45.124 --> 00:10:47.418
All thanks to your hard work
reviewing our product.

00:10:47.501 --> 00:10:48.586
Are you enjoying it?

00:10:50.212 --> 00:10:52.047
-Enjoying what?
-Boyfriend on Demand.

00:10:56.385 --> 00:10:57.303
Well…

00:10:58.554 --> 00:11:02.057
I actually haven't been playing.
I stopped playing back then.

00:11:02.933 --> 00:11:04.185
Is that right?

00:11:04.268 --> 00:11:08.522
You sounded very satisfied in your review.
We even gave you the device.

00:11:08.606 --> 00:11:11.609
I was sure you'd subscribe
once it hit the market.

00:11:12.777 --> 00:11:15.404
I appreciate the gift,
but I've just been busy with life.

00:11:16.155 --> 00:11:20.159
Still, doesn't Boyfriend on Demand
blow real life out of the water?

00:11:23.454 --> 00:11:26.207
I'm not sure.
I'd say real life is still better.

00:11:27.750 --> 00:11:28.918
How heartless of you.

00:11:29.001 --> 00:11:32.755
You can take a look while you're here.
I'll show you around.

00:11:32.838 --> 00:11:33.756
Oh, I can't.

00:11:33.839 --> 00:11:36.592
I'm here for some last-minute shopping,
so I should go.

00:11:38.052 --> 00:11:40.387
I'll see you around, then.

00:11:40.471 --> 00:11:42.056
-Thank you.
-Good luck!

00:11:46.685 --> 00:11:47.937
That was unexpected.

00:11:55.528 --> 00:11:56.362
Hey, what's up?

00:11:56.445 --> 00:11:58.155
You didn't forget, did you?

00:11:58.656 --> 00:12:02.201
Of course not. I'm not a goldfish.
I'm out buying a gift right now.

00:12:02.284 --> 00:12:03.786
That's good to hear.

00:12:04.703 --> 00:12:06.580
I need to tell you something.

00:12:06.664 --> 00:12:09.250
-You do?
-Promise me you won't get mad.

00:12:09.333 --> 00:12:10.459
What is it?

00:12:10.543 --> 00:12:13.712
Someone else will be joining us
at Da-yeong's place today.

00:12:13.796 --> 00:12:14.630
Who?

00:12:15.589 --> 00:12:17.883
Just some guy Da-yeong knows.

00:12:18.926 --> 00:12:20.010
We're setting you up.

00:12:22.805 --> 00:12:23.681
Hello?

00:12:24.807 --> 00:12:26.559
Come on, say something!

00:12:29.478 --> 00:12:31.939
We didn't tell you, and that's on us.

00:12:32.022 --> 00:12:34.984
We were gonna keep it secret
and pretend it was all organic,

00:12:35.568 --> 00:12:40.114
but then we got super worried
that you might show up in sweats.

00:12:41.156 --> 00:12:42.324
Hello?

00:12:43.075 --> 00:12:45.369
Did I screw up again? Are you mad?

00:12:48.122 --> 00:12:48.956
No.

00:12:49.707 --> 00:12:50.541
Huh?

00:12:51.041 --> 00:12:52.042
Well done.

00:12:52.126 --> 00:12:53.294
Well done?

00:12:53.377 --> 00:12:55.462
Yeah. See you later.

00:12:55.546 --> 00:12:56.672
Okay.

00:12:59.925 --> 00:13:00.759
What's with her?

00:13:15.816 --> 00:13:17.484
-Is she running late?
-Don't know!

00:13:17.568 --> 00:13:18.736
Seriously?

00:13:21.363 --> 00:13:23.407
She's always late.
She should be here soon.

00:13:23.991 --> 00:13:24.950
Okay.

00:13:29.830 --> 00:13:30.915
Hey, what…

00:13:32.249 --> 00:13:33.584
Mi-rae, you're here…

00:13:44.511 --> 00:13:45.679
Sorry I'm late.

00:13:45.763 --> 00:13:47.348
Hey, that outfit…

00:13:47.431 --> 00:13:49.808
Hey, this one looks decent.

00:13:52.311 --> 00:13:53.771
Am I wearing this a bit late?

00:13:54.563 --> 00:13:56.482
No. It's meant to be a winter outfit.

00:13:56.565 --> 00:13:57.775
Come in.

00:14:01.278 --> 00:14:03.822
-Shall we have a drink?
-All right.

00:14:03.906 --> 00:14:05.157
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

00:14:09.161 --> 00:14:10.162
Thanks for coming.

00:14:10.245 --> 00:14:12.081
-Totally.
-Of course we came.

00:14:12.164 --> 00:14:14.458
-Have some of this.
-Thank you.

00:14:15.626 --> 00:14:16.669
Is it good?

00:14:16.752 --> 00:14:18.212
-Delicious. So good.
-It's good.

00:14:20.047 --> 00:14:21.048
Here.

00:14:21.548 --> 00:14:22.675
Thank you.

00:14:24.593 --> 00:14:26.595
-A guy with manners.
-Your glass is empty.

00:14:27.262 --> 00:14:28.514
Thank you.

00:14:31.517 --> 00:14:33.143
-Cheers, everyone?
-Sure.

00:14:34.061 --> 00:14:34.979
Cheers!

00:14:35.062 --> 00:14:37.523
APT!

00:14:37.606 --> 00:14:38.440
Seventh floor!

00:14:38.524 --> 00:14:40.985
One. Two. Three. Four. Five. Six. Seven!

00:14:42.194 --> 00:14:44.029
Down the hatch it goes!

00:14:44.113 --> 00:14:44.947
Bunny!

00:14:45.030 --> 00:14:46.031
-Bunny!
-Carrot!

00:14:46.115 --> 00:14:46.949
-Bunny!
-Carrot!

00:14:47.032 --> 00:14:47.992
-Bunny!
-Carrot!

00:14:48.075 --> 00:14:49.076
-Bunny!
-Carrot!

00:14:49.159 --> 00:14:50.202
Carrot…

00:14:51.578 --> 00:14:52.579
I'll drink that.

00:14:53.163 --> 00:14:54.498
So sweet!

00:14:59.253 --> 00:15:00.421
Seo Mi-rae won again.

00:15:00.504 --> 00:15:01.755
You two are so good.

00:15:01.839 --> 00:15:03.257
I want my boyfriend here now.

00:15:03.340 --> 00:15:04.717
Hey, you don't mean…

00:15:05.217 --> 00:15:06.552
Hey!

00:15:06.635 --> 00:15:09.138
-Are you okay? Where are the napkins?
-Are you okay?

00:15:10.014 --> 00:15:11.932
Good thing you didn't get drenched.

00:15:12.016 --> 00:15:13.225
Thank you.

00:15:13.308 --> 00:15:14.268
This is going well.

00:15:17.563 --> 00:15:19.064
Happy, Mi-rae?

00:15:21.025 --> 00:15:22.026
Cheers.

00:15:22.109 --> 00:15:23.527
Let's drink, guys.

00:15:23.610 --> 00:15:25.029
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

00:15:26.363 --> 00:15:27.865
I had a great time today.

00:15:30.034 --> 00:15:33.037
I'm quite an introvert,
but you made me feel comfortable,

00:15:33.120 --> 00:15:34.872
so I enjoyed it a lot too.

00:15:34.955 --> 00:15:37.291
Really? That's nice to hear.

00:15:38.500 --> 00:15:41.378
Da-yeong said
a lot of great things about you.

00:15:42.046 --> 00:15:45.591
Now that I've met you,
you do seem like a really nice person.

00:15:45.674 --> 00:15:46.717
And you're cute.

00:15:49.136 --> 00:15:50.471
What did you think?

00:15:51.096 --> 00:15:51.930
Sorry?

00:15:52.431 --> 00:15:53.307
Of me.

00:15:56.018 --> 00:15:57.895
I also had a good time.

00:15:58.520 --> 00:16:01.315
That's good. Does that mean
we can see each other again?

