00:41:54.992 --> 00:41:55.826
Thanks.

00:42:03.709 --> 00:42:05.461
I see you're buying just a cup today.

00:42:06.211 --> 00:42:07.046
Excuse me?

00:42:08.130 --> 00:42:11.550
Last time, you bought another one
to drink on your way home.

00:42:14.762 --> 00:42:16.597
Here's your iced latte.

00:42:19.350 --> 00:42:21.602
Buying two wasn't necessary today.

00:42:24.188 --> 00:42:26.982
Hwany must be late with his file today.
How unusual.

00:42:28.233 --> 00:42:30.611
It looks like he's going hard this week.

00:42:36.241 --> 00:42:37.242
Is that so?

00:42:37.743 --> 00:42:40.329
Still, I doubt we're going to beat TMTK.

00:42:41.580 --> 00:42:44.416
I guess it's another late submission
with Ms. Yun tonight.

00:42:48.253 --> 00:42:49.088
No.

00:42:49.171 --> 00:42:52.299
We are also going hard this week, you see.

00:42:53.842 --> 00:42:55.302
Oh, is that right?

00:42:56.595 --> 00:42:58.681
Here's your Americano.

00:43:12.361 --> 00:43:13.195
I need a straw.

00:43:33.632 --> 00:43:35.426
It's about time you sent it. Come on.

00:43:45.144 --> 00:43:46.145
I'm heading out first.

00:43:47.730 --> 00:43:48.981
Sure. Good night.

00:43:49.064 --> 00:43:50.774
Right. Good luck.

00:43:58.115 --> 00:43:59.450
What am I going to do?

00:43:59.908 --> 00:44:00.743
YUN SONG

00:44:07.332 --> 00:44:08.167
UPLOAD COMPLETE

00:44:12.171 --> 00:44:13.547
I'm home.

00:44:13.630 --> 00:44:15.299
Initiating home mode.

00:44:19.845 --> 00:44:21.346
God, I'm wiped out.

00:44:27.561 --> 00:44:28.562
Let's see now.

00:44:39.531 --> 00:44:41.825
-Is the spelling for real?
-It has to be a joke.

00:44:41.909 --> 00:44:43.243
The worst typo ever.

00:44:43.327 --> 00:44:45.078
Doesn't Naemo even have an editor?

00:44:45.162 --> 00:44:47.915
Choi Si-woo goes out in a blaze of idiocy.
God save him!

00:44:50.417 --> 00:44:53.212
"Sorry to brother you,
but I'll be taking this woman."

00:44:54.463 --> 00:44:55.297
"Brother"?

00:44:56.215 --> 00:44:57.591
What am I looking at?

00:44:57.674 --> 00:44:59.343
Are you kidding me?!

00:44:59.426 --> 00:45:01.428
BROTHER

00:45:11.313 --> 00:45:13.482
Excuse me, sir?

00:45:13.565 --> 00:45:14.566
I'm sorry.

00:45:15.692 --> 00:45:18.111
So he "brothers" to take her away,

00:45:18.195 --> 00:45:20.405
buys her a giant diamond ring,
and proposes?

00:45:23.992 --> 00:45:25.327
Have you

00:45:25.410 --> 00:45:26.745
completely lost it?

00:45:28.205 --> 00:45:31.083
I should have checked more carefully.
This is my fault.

00:45:31.166 --> 00:45:33.627
How can I not be "brothered" right now?

00:45:34.920 --> 00:45:38.090
I'm dying from embarrassment
because of you, seriously!

00:45:40.509 --> 00:45:43.053
-Don't "brother" me. Just move.
-Right.

00:45:43.637 --> 00:45:45.097
I need some sugar. Damn it.

00:45:45.180 --> 00:45:46.974
Goodbye, sir.

00:45:47.057 --> 00:45:49.268
Has anyone got a macaron or something?

00:45:49.852 --> 00:45:52.688
God, I'm so freaking embarrassed!

00:46:00.195 --> 00:46:01.530
So embarrassing.

00:46:14.543 --> 00:46:17.880
Sorry to "brother" you,
but may I pass through?

00:46:17.963 --> 00:46:19.506
Oh, sure.

00:46:20.966 --> 00:46:22.009
Thank you.

00:46:27.139 --> 00:46:28.223
Did he say "brother"?

00:46:51.038 --> 00:46:52.831
Why did I act like such a child?

00:47:00.505 --> 00:47:01.757
Man, I'm beat.

00:47:14.686 --> 00:47:15.896
That hits the spot.

00:47:19.691 --> 00:47:20.692
Ms. Yun.

00:47:20.776 --> 00:47:23.820
From now on, please send the file
before 7 p.m. without exception.

00:47:23.904 --> 00:47:25.238
I'm not asking.

00:47:25.322 --> 00:47:27.157
I'm going to die of embarrassment.

00:47:27.240 --> 00:47:29.159
For the love of…

00:47:29.660 --> 00:47:31.662
Why is she lashing out at me so early?

00:47:31.745 --> 00:47:33.080
What's the fuss about?

00:47:38.460 --> 00:47:41.338
Sorry to brother you,
but I'll be taking this woman.

00:47:45.801 --> 00:47:46.969
What's wrong with it?

00:47:52.849 --> 00:47:55.727
-Proof that she lives on IG.
-The man to know doesn't know much.

00:47:55.811 --> 00:47:57.521
-How are you an author?
-Airhead.

00:47:57.604 --> 00:47:59.106
Take some Korean lessons, please.

00:47:59.189 --> 00:48:00.899
See? You can be dumb and loaded.

00:48:00.983 --> 00:48:02.693
Don't be so harsh. She can't help it.

00:48:02.776 --> 00:48:05.278
Who do you think you all are, King Sejong?

00:48:07.447 --> 00:48:10.283
If you don't want to read it,
just don't read it!

00:48:12.160 --> 00:48:13.745
Seriously!

00:48:17.374 --> 00:48:18.333
BOYFRIEND ON DEMAND

00:48:18.417 --> 00:48:19.292
What's this?

00:48:40.480 --> 00:48:41.565
Look who it is.

00:48:42.065 --> 00:48:43.650
What are you up to? Where are you?

00:48:43.734 --> 00:48:45.110
I'm hanging out with Da-yeong.

00:48:45.193 --> 00:48:48.864
What? You two met up?
Without telling me about it?

00:48:49.531 --> 00:48:52.325
You kept ignoring our messages.
We figured you were busy.

00:48:53.118 --> 00:48:55.203
You must be free now,
calling me like this.

00:48:56.038 --> 00:48:56.955
Are you mad?

00:48:57.706 --> 00:48:59.082
No, I mean…

00:48:59.833 --> 00:49:02.169
Don't be. I'm going through a lot.

00:49:02.919 --> 00:49:04.838
Where are you? Can I join you guys?

00:49:06.173 --> 00:49:08.717
-My boyfriend and Jun-ho will be here.
-Tell her to come.

00:49:08.800 --> 00:49:10.552
Want to come? You're welcome to join.

00:49:10.635 --> 00:49:13.180
So it's a double date.

00:49:14.097 --> 00:49:15.515
Nah, I'll pass.

00:49:15.599 --> 00:49:17.059
Okay. Stay in touch.

00:49:17.142 --> 00:49:18.435
Yeah.

00:49:27.694 --> 00:49:29.237
I want to get away.

00:50:04.481 --> 00:50:08.693
Ms. Seo Mi-rae, would you like to go
and meet your new date?

00:50:08.777 --> 00:50:11.530
I said I'll pass today.
My subscription's nearly over anyway.

00:50:14.574 --> 00:50:15.575
What the…

00:50:18.370 --> 00:50:19.496
What is this?

00:50:24.835 --> 00:50:28.004
This is driving me crazy.
I said I'll pass.

00:51:03.874 --> 00:51:04.958
An office worker?

00:51:11.089 --> 00:51:12.549
Nice weather.

00:52:03.683 --> 00:52:04.517
Seo Mi-rae.

00:52:29.626 --> 00:52:30.460
Is it you?

00:52:33.088 --> 00:52:34.339
How…

00:52:35.924 --> 00:52:37.634
It's been so long.

00:52:39.219 --> 00:52:40.637
Has it been ten years?

00:52:40.720 --> 00:52:42.555
He's not a college student anymore.

00:52:44.557 --> 00:52:46.142
SPRING, AND YOU

00:52:46.226 --> 00:52:47.602
"To be continued"?

00:52:59.489 --> 00:53:00.991
So what happened?

00:53:01.908 --> 00:53:02.742
What?

00:53:03.785 --> 00:53:05.704
I was worried when you disappeared.

00:53:09.499 --> 00:53:10.333
Well…

00:53:10.417 --> 00:53:11.710
Have you been well?

00:53:13.837 --> 00:53:17.841
I knew it was just a ploy
to get me to extend my subscription,

00:53:18.800 --> 00:53:20.427
but having seen Seo Eun-ho…

00:53:25.223 --> 00:53:26.057
I have.

00:53:27.600 --> 00:53:28.768
How about you?

00:53:29.728 --> 00:53:30.562
Me too.

00:53:32.522 --> 00:53:34.065
…I had to fall for it again.

00:53:34.566 --> 00:53:37.152
You've changed a lot, Mi-rae.

00:53:39.404 --> 00:53:40.280
Have I?

00:53:41.656 --> 00:53:42.490
You too.

00:53:44.909 --> 00:53:46.745
It's been ten years, after all.

00:53:50.248 --> 00:53:51.458
But you are…

00:53:54.419 --> 00:53:56.880
still as pretty as ever.

00:54:23.698 --> 00:54:24.532
Welcome…

00:54:25.116 --> 00:54:27.744
Oh my God, is there a fire somewhere?

00:54:27.827 --> 00:54:30.830
Yes. Fortunately,
we managed to put out the worst of it.

00:54:31.623 --> 00:54:32.582
That's good to hear.

00:54:32.665 --> 00:54:34.834
There's still a fire that won't go out.

00:54:35.502 --> 00:54:36.920
What? Where is it?

00:54:41.049 --> 00:54:42.092
It's burning

00:54:42.884 --> 00:54:44.219
in my heart for you.

00:54:48.598 --> 00:54:51.976
Mi-rae, I've spent my whole life
putting out fires.

00:54:52.477 --> 00:54:54.354
But this fire burning for you?

00:54:55.480 --> 00:54:56.481
I never

00:54:57.148 --> 00:54:58.400
want to put it out.

00:55:06.699 --> 00:55:08.660
WOULD YOU LIKE TO MEET
YOUR NEXT BOYFRIEND?

00:55:08.743 --> 00:55:09.577
YES

00:57:17.080 --> 00:57:22.085
Subtitle translation by: Daham Yoon